---
import MarketingLayout from '../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---
<MarketingLayout title="FAQ | Website Factory" description="Answers for local business owners considering the service.">
  <section class="content-section"><div class="container prose">
    <h1>FAQ</h1>
    <h2>Is this a custom-coded site?</h2><p>It is a tailored implementation built on a proven static template system.</p>
    <h2>What do I need to provide?</h2><p>Business info, services, location coverage, contact details, and any photos/logo assets you have.</p>
    <h2>Do you handle hosting?</h2><p>Yes. We can launch to Cloudflare Pages, Netlify, or GitHub Pages.</p>
  </div></section>
</MarketingLayout>
